### 关于js
- 0：数据结构；统一转为时间戳处理，显示的时候转为具体时间；

``` 
[
{
	start: 0,
	end: 7200000,
	list: [
		0,
		900000,
		1800000,
		2700000,
		3600000,
		4500000,
		5400000,
		6300000
	]
}
] 

estimatedTime = { //选择到的预约时间, 
	start: 0,
	end: 7200000,
	list: [
		0,
		900000,
		1800000,
		2700000,
		3600000,
		4500000,
		5400000,
		6300000
	]
} 
```

- 1：获取门店的营业时间(工作日营业时间；周六周日营业时间)；

```
	//将 10:00:00 转为 时间戳
    if (storeInfos.isHoliday) {
      start = this.toTimeStr(storeInfos.holiday_business_time);
      end = this.toTimeStr(storeInfos.holiday_close_time);
    } else {
      start = this.toTimeStr(storeInfos.work_business_time);
      end = this.toTimeStr(storeInfos.work_close_time);
    }
```

- 2：预约时间的区间为两小时，整理从门店开店时间到关店时间的时间段。

```
	//时间段 ： [时间戳],中间间隔2小时
    let timeList = [];
    for (let i = start; i < end; i = i + 2 * 1000 * 60 * 60) {
      timeList.push(i);
    }
    timeList.push(end);
```

- 3：生成初始化数据结构

```
    //0.默认为当前时间，即（现在下单），estimatedTime为空
    //1.生成可用的时间区间列表 {start:'',end:'',list:[]}
    //2.小的区间间隔为15分钟
    let targetTimeList = [];
    for (let i = 0; i < timeList.length; i++) {
      let list = [];
      for (let j = timeList[i]; j < timeList[i + 1]; j = j + 15 * 1000 * 60) {
        list.push(j);
      }
      if (!!timeList[i + 1]) {
        targetTimeList.push({
          start: timeList[i],
          end: timeList[i + 1],
          list: list
        })
      }
    }
```

- 4：获取当前时间，整理出可预约的时间数据；（预约规则：堂食60分钟后才能预约；外卖30分钟后才能预约；）

```
    //1.获取当前时间的时间戳
    let currentTime = new Date().toTimeString().substr(0, 8);
        currentTime = this.toTimeStr(currentTime); //转为时间戳
    //2.判断当前是否为外卖
    let take_out_att = 0;
    try {
      const value = wx.getStorageSync('take_out_att');
      if (value) {
        take_out_att = value;
        this.setData({
          take_out_att:value
        })
      }
    } catch (e) {
      // Do something when catch error
    }
    //2.1：自取提前一个小时
    currentTime = currentTime + 60 * 60 * 1000;
    //2.2：外卖提前半个小时
    if (take_out_att == 1){ 
      let newShijianchuo = this.data.newShijianchuo;
      newShijianchuo = new Date(newShijianchuo * 1000).toTimeString().substr(0, 8);
      newShijianchuo = this.toTimeStr(newShijianchuo);
      currentTime = newShijianchuo + 30 * 60 * 1000
    }
    //3.过滤出当前可用的时间数据，如果在当前区间，加个选中的状态
    let list = targetTimeList;
    let newList = [];
    for(let i = 0;i<list.length; i++){  
      list[i].active = false;
      if (currentTime >= list[i].start && currentTime < list[i].end) {
        list[i].active = true;
        list[i].list = list[i].list.filter(h => {
          return h >= currentTime;
        });
        newList = list.slice(i);
        break;
      }
    }
    //4.判断当前是否有可预约的时间
    let isActiveArr = newList.filter(v=>{ 
        return v.active == true;
    })
    if (!isActiveArr.length){ 
        wx.showToast({
          title: '当前无可预约时间',
          icon:'none'
        });
        this.close(); //关闭预约时间的弹窗
        return;
    }
    //4.1:关闭的时候 获取当前选中的预约时间
    close() {
      if (this.data.value == '现在下单' || this.data.value == ''){ 
        this.triggerEvent('closeappointment', {
          appointmentObj: {
            value: '',       //选中的时间值
            firstindex: 0, //左侧选中区间的索引值
            twoindex: 0 //右侧选中区间的索引值
          }
        });
      }else{
        this.triggerEvent('closeappointment', {
          appointmentObj: {
            value: this.data.value,
            firstindex: this.data.firstindex,
            twoindex: this.data.twoindex
          }
        });
      }
    }
    //5.将时间戳 转为 时间字符串，用于页面展示
    newList.forEach(v => {
        v.start = this.toLocalTime(v.start);
        v.end = this.toLocalTime(v.end);
        for (let j = 0; j < v.list.length; j++) {
          v.list[j] = this.toLocalTime(v.list[j]);
        }
    });
    newList[0].list.unshift('现在下单');
    newList[0].current = 0;
    //5.1:判断列表中是否有选中的时间
     this.isSelectItem(newList);
     isSelectItem(currentList) {
      //newAppointmentObj 为当前选中的时间。
      if (this.data.newAppointmentObj && !!Object.keys(this.data.newAppointmentObj).length) {
        let newAppointmentObj = this.data.newAppointmentObj;
        let newCurrentList = [];
        for (let i = 0; i < currentList.length; i++) {
          //初始化数据
          currentList[i].active = false;
          delete currentList[i].current;
          if (i == newAppointmentObj.firstindex) {
            currentList[i].active = true;
            currentList[i].current = newAppointmentObj.twoindex;
          }
        }
      }
      return currentList;
    }
   //5.2:处理时间戳=》转为时间
    toLocalTime(v) {
      let h = parseInt(v / 1000 / 60 / 60 % 24);
      let m = parseInt(v / 1000 / 60 % 60);
      if (h === 0){ 
        h = '00'
      } else if (10>h>0){ 
        h = '0' + h;
      }
      if (m === 0) {
        m = '00'
      } else if (10 > m > 0) {
        m = '0' + m;
      }
      v = `${h}:${m}`;
      return v;
    }
    toTimeStr(time) {
      let itemStr = 0;
      let timeArr = time.split(':');
      let h = timeArr[0] * 1000 * 60 * 60;
      let m = timeArr[1] * 1000 * 60;
      let s = timeArr[2] * 1000;
      itemStr = h + m + s;
      return itemStr;
    }
```
